    MTLSController -->|depends on| CertManager["cert-manager"]
    HeadPod -->|optional| Volcano["Volcano / Yunikorn<br/>(batch scheduling)"]

    %% Integration points
    Prometheus["Prometheus"] -->|scrapes 8080/TCP| KubeRayOperator
    RhodsOp["rhods-operator"] -->|deploys via kustomize| KubeRayOperator

